 ### `SharedMemory.createChannel(pool, options)` _Experimental_
 
@@ -58,9 +58,11 @@ usage.
 
 Creates a sending `SharedMemoryChannel` endpoint backed by `pool`.
 
-The current implementation is intended for renderer-to-main streaming. Create
-the sending endpoint in the renderer and create a matching receiving endpoint in
